<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>404 - Page Not Found</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            background-color: #f5f7fa;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .container {
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
        }
        .circles {
            position: absolute;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            z-index: -1;
        }
        .circle {
            position: absolute;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
        }
        .circle-1 { width: 200px; height: 200px; background: #a3bffa; top: 10%; left: 10%; }
        .circle-2 { width: 150px; height: 150px; background: #ffcccc; top: 20%; right: 10%; }
        .circle-3 { width: 100px; height: 100px; background: #ffe6cc; bottom: 20%; left: 20%; }
        .circle-4 { width: 120px; height: 120px; background: #d4c4fb; bottom: 10%; right: 15%; }
        h1 {
            font-size: 120px;
            color: #ff6b6b;
            margin: 0;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        h2 {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #333;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        p {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        a {
            text-decoration: none;
            background-color: #ff6b6b;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }
        a:hover {
            background-color: #e65b5b;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="circles">
            <div class="circle circle-1"></div>
            <div class="circle circle-2"></div>
            <div class="circle circle-3"></div>
            <div class="circle circle-4"></div>
        </div>
        <h1>404</h1>
        <h2>Page not found</h2>
        <p>Oops! The page you are looking for does not exist. It might have been moved or deleted.</p>
        <a href="/">Back to Home</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>